name: eTranscriber Transcription Services
tag_list: transcription-serivces, mp3-transcription-serivces, audio-transcription, video-transcription, interview-transcription, digital-transcription, conference-transcription
overview:
eTranscriber is a transcription service provider for all types of audio and video.

Transcriptions are done by experts and trained transcriptionists with a high degree of accuracy. Transcription rates start at a nominal 0.75$ which is claimed to be the cheapest and the lowest for transcription services.

eTranscriber.net has served a large number of clients, some of which include doctors, corporate CEO’s, Interviewers, Radio station broadcasters and independent journalists.
